WEBVTT


00:00:00.280 --> 00:00:02.440
Big news from Spain's Supreme Court

00:00:02.440 --> 00:00:04.040
the six month stay rule for

00:00:04.040 --> 00:00:05.680
temporary residence has been axed

00:00:05.680 --> 00:00:08.040
starting March 4th, 2024

00:00:08.040 --> 00:00:11.100
after an appeal against the 2019 government resolution

00:00:11.320 --> 00:00:13.680
no more worrying about losing your temporary residence

00:00:13.680 --> 00:00:16.140
for spending over six months outside Spain.

00:00:16.280 --> 00:00:18.520
This change is gonna bring relief to current residents

00:00:18.520 --> 00:00:20.900
and simplifies the process for applicants.

00:00:20.920 --> 00:00:21.800
But remember,

00:00:21.800 --> 00:00:24.340
you still need to meet the other requirements.

00:00:24.640 --> 00:00:26.360
If you need any help whatsoever

00:00:26.360 --> 00:00:27.800
with your immigration needs,

00:00:27.800 --> 00:00:30.460
don't hesitate to contact just law solicitors.
